metadata.title: Set of 2 DOG BREED Shatterproof Designer 16 oz Plastic Wine Glasses MADE in the USA (SIBERIAN HUSKY)
features: Set of 2 PET SHATTERPROOF and STEMLESS plastic wine glasses featuring custom assorted designs.
Perfect for the beach, boating, poolside, camping, tailgating, the front porch, vacations and cruises and more...
Made in the USA, Recyclable and BPA Free, 16 oz Capacity, Crystal Clear, Perfect fit for the hand!
High quality, heavyweight and durable. Use and over again! HAND WASH only! Best thing of all, you can safely take this wine tumbler everywhere!
Packaged in a fun, colorful, custom box. Makes a great gift!
